d then I will follow you.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:21–22","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":21,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 8:21–22","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Ki:19:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So he turned back from following him, took the team of oxen, and slaughtered "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or sacrificed"},{"kind":"text","text":" them. With the oxen’s wooden yoke and plow, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 6:14","book":"1Sa","chapter":6,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 24:22","book":"2Sa","chapter":24,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" he cooked the meat and gave it to the people, and they ate. Then he left, followed Elijah, and served him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:26","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 14:33","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":33,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 6:14","book":"1Sa","chapter":6,"verse":14},{"label":"2Sm 24:22","book":"2Sa","chapter":24,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 14:26","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":26},{"label":"Lk 14:33","book":"Luk","chapter":14,"verse":33}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or sacrificed"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099308405}